com.friendlyreminder.application.contactbook

Class ContactBook

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.friendlyreminder.application.contactbook.ContactBook

  • @Entity
public class ContactBook
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents a contact book. It contains a list of Contacts - This class is saved to Relational Database according to Hibernate annotations - The contact list in the contact book is sorted by one of ContactListSortingStrategy strategies
